 map space vs. sort + two pointers)\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\n\\u003ch3\\u003eFollow-up questions they may ask\\u003c/h3\\u003e\\n\\u003cul\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eCan you solve it with less memory?\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eWhat if the input stream is infinite / doesn't fit in RAM?\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eHow would tests look for adversarial inputs?\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\n23:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",\\\"interview\\\",{\\\"id\\\":\\\"interview\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-10 scroll-mt-24\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-bold\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Interview Walkthrough\\\"}],false]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"prose-af\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"$33\\\"}}]]}]\\n24:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",\\\"optimized\\\",{\\\"id\\\":\\\"optimized\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-10 scroll-mt-24\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-bold\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Optimized Approach\\\"}],false]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"prose-af\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"\\u003ch2\\u003eOptimized solution notes\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\\\n\\u003cp\\u003eThe reference solutions on AlgoForge target \\u003cstrong\\u003eO(n)\\u003c/strong\\u003e time and \\u003cstrong\\u003eO(1)\\u003c/strong\\u003e space.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\\\n\\u003ch3\\u003ePattern focus: general problem-solving\\u003c/h3\\u003e\\\\n\\u003cp\\u003eUse the pattern as a checklist:\\u003c/p\\u003e\\\\n\\u003cul\\u003e\\\\n\\u003cli\\u003eIdentify the dominant pattern and stick to one clear invariant\\u003c/li\\u003e\\\\n\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\\\n\\u003cp\\u003eStart from the primary solution, 